snippet.title: The Guild of Thieves (1987) (Rainbird)
snippet.description:
Partial playthrough of The Guild of Thieves, running on the Pi under ADFFS.  I didn't have the manual to hand..so had to stop at the protection check

One of the Magnetic Scrolls adventures, which included Corruption, Fish!, The Guild of Thieves, Jinxter, The Pawn and Wonderland
